sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the Russell 3000 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Pjt Partners Inc Class A (Symbol: PJT), where a total volume of 1,252 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 125,200 underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 89.8% of PJT's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 139,445 shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $55 strike call option expiring June 19, 2020, with 1,106 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 110,600 underlying shares of PJT.
